Module OOP
Package OOPProject

Class AppConfig

java.lang.Object
OOPProject.AppConfig
public class AppConfig extends Object
This class holds the file paths for various CSV files used in the application. It is a utility class providing constants for file locations.

Each constant in this class points to a specific CSV file required for the operations of the Hospital App, including files for diagnosis, prescription, treatment, medication, patient records, doctor details, and appointment data.

All file paths are specified relative to the source folder of the project.

Example:

    AppConfig.DIAGNOSIS_FILE_PATH;
